    "Rinse the eggplant slices and pat them dry with paper towels.",
    "Set up three shallow dishes: one with flour, one with beaten eggs, and one with breadcrumbs.",
    "Dredge each eggplant slice in the flour, then dip it into the beaten eggs, and coat it evenly with breadcrumbs. Repeat with all slices.",
