    "Stir in the butter, grated Parmesan cheese, chopped fresh parsley, and lemon zest until well combined.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Remove from heat and let the risotto rest for a few minutes before serving.",
    "Garnish with additional chopped parsley and lemon wedges, if desired.",
    "Serve the seafood risotto hot, and enjoy!"
]

